      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-low heat</p>\r\n<p>Once hot, add the <strong>chilled patties</strong> and cook for 4-5 min on each side or until browned on both sides</p>",
